msgid "# PD-Colocated with Mooncake Multi-Instance"
msgstr "# 基于Mooncake多实例的PD共置部署"

msgid "## Getting Started"
msgstr "## 快速开始"

msgid ""
"vLLM-Ascend now supports PD-colocated deployment with Mooncake features.\n"
"This guide provides step-by-step instructions to test these features with\n"
"constrained resources."
msgstr ""
"vLLM-Ascend 现已支持基于 Mooncake 特性的 PD 共置部署。\n"
"本指南提供在资源受限条件下测试这些功能的分步说明。"

msgid ""
"Using the Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct model as an example, this guide demonstrates\n"
"how to use vllm-ascend {{vllm_ascend_version}} (with vLLM {{vllm_version}}) on two Atlas 800T A2\n"
"nodes to deploy two vLLM instances. Each instance occupies 4 NPU cards and\n"
"uses PD-colocated deployment."
msgstr ""
"以 Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct 模型为例，本指南演示如何在两台 Atlas 800T A2\n"
"节点上使用 vllm-ascend {{vllm_ascend_version}}（基于 vLLM {{vllm_version}}）部署两个 vLLM 实例。\n"
"每个实例占用 4 张 NPU 卡，并采用 PD 共置部署方式。"

msgid "## Verify Multi-Node Communication Environment"
msgstr "## 验证多节点通信环境"

msgid "### Physical Layer Requirements"
msgstr "### 物理层要求"

msgid ""
"- The two Atlas 800T A2 nodes must be physically interconnected via a RoCE\n"
"  network. Without RoCE interconnection, cross-node KV Cache access\n"
"  performance will be significantly degraded.\n"
"- All NPU cards must communicate properly. Intra-node communication uses HCCS,\n"
"  while inter-node communication uses the RoCE network."
msgstr ""
"- 两台 Atlas 800T A2 节点必须通过 RoCE 网络进行物理互联。\n"
"  若无 RoCE 互联，跨节点 KV Cache 访问性能将显著下降。\n"
"- 所有 NPU 卡必须正常通信。节点内通信使用 HCCS，\n"
"  节点间通信使用 RoCE 网络。"

msgid "### Verification Process"
msgstr "### 验证流程"

msgid ""
"The following process serves as a reference example. Please modify parameters\n"
"such as IP addresses according to your actual environment."
msgstr "以下流程作为参考示例。请根据实际环境修改 IP 地址等参数。"

msgid "1. Single Node Verification:"
msgstr "1. 单节点验证："

msgid ""
"Execute the following commands sequentially. The results must all be\n"
"   `success` and the status must be `UP`:"
msgstr ""
"依次执行以下命令。结果必须全部为\n"
"   `success`，且状态必须为 `UP`："

msgid "2. Check NPU HCCN Configuration:"
msgstr "2. 检查 NPU HCCN 配置："

msgid ""
"Ensure that the hccn.conf file exists in the environment. If using Docker,\n"
"   mount it into the container."
msgstr ""
"确保环境中存在 hccn.conf 文件。如果使用 Docker，\n"
"   请将其挂载到容器中。"

msgid "3. Get NPU IP Addresses:"
msgstr "3. 获取 NPU IP 地址："

msgid "4. Cross-Node PING Test:"
msgstr "4. 跨节点 PING 测试："

msgid "5. Check NPU TLS Configuration"
msgstr "5. 检查 NPU TLS 配置"

msgid "## Run with Docker"
msgstr "## 使用 Docker 运行"

msgid "Start a Docker container on each node."
msgstr "在每个节点上启动一个 Docker 容器。"

msgid "## (Optional) Install Mooncake"
msgstr "## （可选）安装 Mooncake"

msgid ""
"Mooncake is pre-installed and functional in the {{vllm_ascend_version}} image.\n"
"The following installation steps are optional."
msgstr ""
"Mooncake 已在 {{vllm_ascend_version}} 镜像中预装并可正常使用。\n"
"以下安装步骤为可选操作。"

msgid ""
"Mooncake is the serving platform for Kimi, a leading LLM service provided by\n"
"Moonshot AI. Installation and compilation guide:\n"
"<https://github.com/kvcache-ai/Mooncake?tab=readme-ov-file#build-and-use-binaries>."
msgstr ""
"Mooncake 是 Moonshot AI 旗下领先的大语言模型服务 Kimi 的推理平台。\n"
"安装与编译指南：\n"
"<https://github.com/kvcache-ai/Mooncake?tab=readme-ov-file#build-and-use-binaries>。"

