msgstr "mooncake.json 文件的模板如下："

msgid "## vLLM Instance Deployment"
msgstr "## vLLM 实例部署"

msgid ""
"Create containers on both Node 1 and Node 2, and launch the\n"
"Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct model service in each to test the reusability and\n"
"performance of cross-node, cross-instance KV Cache. Instance 1 utilizes NPU\n"
"cards [0-3] on the first Atlas 800T A2 server, while Instance 2 utilizes\n"
"cards [0-3] on the second server."
msgstr ""
"在节点 1 和节点 2 上分别创建容器，并在每个容器中启动\n"
"Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct 模型服务，以测试跨节点、跨实例 KV Cache 的\n"
"可复用性和性能。实例 1 使用第一台 Atlas 800T A2 服务器上的 NPU\n"
"卡 [0-3]，实例 2 使用第二台服务器上的卡 [0-3]。"

msgid "### Deploy Instance 1"
msgstr "### 部署实例 1"

msgid ""
"Replace file paths, host, and port parameters based on your actual environment\n"
"configuration."
msgstr "根据实际环境配置替换文件路径、host 和 port 参数。"

msgid "### Deploy Instance 2"
msgstr "### 部署实例 2"

msgid ""
"The deployment method for Instance 2 is identical to Instance 1. Simply\n"
"modify the `--host` and `--port` parameters according to your Instance 2\n"
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"实例 2 的部署方法与实例 1 相同。只需根据实例 2 的配置\n"
"修改 `--host` 和 `--port` 参数即可。"

msgid "### Configuration Parameters"
msgstr "### 配置参数"

msgid "**Note on use_layerwise:**"
msgstr "**关于 use_layerwise 的说明：**"

msgid ""
"- `false`: Transfer entire KV Cache (suitable for cross-node with sufficient\n"
"  bandwidth)\n"
"- `true`: Layer-by-layer transfer (suitable for single-node memory\n"
"  constraints)"
msgstr ""
"- `false`：传输整个 KV Cache（适用于带宽充足的跨节点场景）\n"
"- `true`：逐层传输（适用于单节点内存受限的场景）"

msgid "## Benchmark"
msgstr "## 基准测试"

msgid ""
"We recommend using the **AISBench** tool to assess performance. The test uses\n"
"**Dataset A**, consisting of fully random data, with the following\n"
"configuration:"
msgstr ""
"建议使用 **AISBench** 工具评估性能。测试使用完全随机的\n"
"**数据集 A**，配置如下："

msgid ""
"- Input/output tokens: 1024/10\n"
"- Total requests: 100\n"
"- Concurrency: 25"
msgstr ""
"- 输入/输出 tokens：1024/10\n"
"- 总请求数：100\n"
"- 并发数：25"

msgid "The test procedure consists of three steps:"
msgstr "测试流程包含三个步骤："

msgid "### Step 1: Baseline (No Cache)"
msgstr "### 步骤1：基准测试（无缓存）"

msgid ""
"Send Dataset A to Instance 1 on Node 1 and record the Time to First Token\n"
"(TTFT) as **TTFT1**."
msgstr ""
"将数据集A发送至节点1上的实例1，记录首Token时间\n"
"（TTFT）为 **TTFT1**。"

msgid "### Preparation for Step 2"
msgstr "### 步骤2准备"

msgid ""
"Before Step 2, send a fully random Dataset B to Instance 1. Due to the\n"
"unified on-chip memory/DRAM KV Cache with LRU (Least Recently Used) eviction policy,\n"
"Dataset B's cache evicts Dataset A's cache from on-chip memory, leaving Dataset A's\n"
"cache only in Node 1's DRAM."
msgstr ""
"在步骤2之前，将完全随机的数据集B发送至实例1。由于采用LRU（最近最少使用）淘汰策略的统一\n"
"片上内存/DRAM KV缓存，数据集B的缓存会将数据集A的缓存从片上内存中淘汰，使得数据集A的\n"
"缓存仅保留在节点1的DRAM中。"

msgid "### Step 2: Local DRAM Hit"
msgstr "### 步骤2：本地DRAM命中"

msgid ""
"Send Dataset A to Instance 1 again to measure the performance when hitting\n"
"the KV Cache in local DRAM. Record the TTFT as **TTFT2**."
msgstr ""
"再次将数据集A发送至实例1，以测量命中本地DRAM中KV缓存时的性能。\n"
"记录TTFT为 **TTFT2**。"

msgid "### Step 3: Cross-Node DRAM Hit"
msgstr "### 步骤3：跨节点DRAM命中"

msgid ""
"Send Dataset A to Instance 2. With the Mooncake KV Cache pool, this results\n"
"in a cross-node KV Cache hit from Node 1's DRAM. Record the TTFT as\n"
"**TTFT3**."
msgstr ""
"将数据集A发送至实例2。借助Mooncake KV缓存池，这将实现从节点1的DRAM\n"
"跨节点命中KV缓存。记录TTFT为 **TTFT3**。"

